I tried to assign the start of the word to the shapes, like "zeti" for the explosion, "wopi" to the circle, and so on. I also noticed that when the color of the shape was grey, the word would normally end with "coe" instead of "koe". 

I didn't use paper to take notes.

The hardest part were trying to remember the end of the word. If it ends with "koe" or "coe". But "koe" was way more common.
